<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-6904] AIC in Closure is checked for wrong constructor</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-6904</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;interface&lt;/span&gt; X {
    def m()
}

@groovy.transform.CompileStatic
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;A {
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Object&lt;/span&gt; pm = &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;pm&quot;&lt;/span&gt;

    def bar(Closure&amp;lt;? exends X&amp;gt; x) {x().m()}
    def foo() {
        bar { -&amp;gt;
            &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; X() {
                def m() {
                    print pm.getClass().getSimpleName()
                }
            }
        }
    }
}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This fails with &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Cannot call A$1#&amp;lt;init&amp;gt;(groovy.lang.Closure) with arguments &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;A&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;and &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Cannot find matching method A#bar(groovy.lang.Closure &amp;lt;A$1&amp;gt;). Please check if the declared type is right and if the method exists.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;but it should work&lt;/p&gt;</description>
